### [é‡å†™å±æ€§ (Overriding Properties)](https://docs.swift.org/swift-book/documentation/the-swift-programming-language/inheritance#Overriding-Properties)
#### [é‡å†™å±æ€§çš„ Getters å’Œ Setters (Overriding Property Getters and Setters)](https://docs.swift.org/swift-book/documentation/the-swift-programming-language/inheritance#Overriding-Property-Getters-and-Setters)

åˆ¤æ–­æ˜¯å¦å±äºé‡å†™çš„ä¾æ®æ˜¯å±æ€§åå’Œå…¶ç±»å‹:
```swift
